<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A Thokit Tai</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. En un, a khai ui melmaten,
 Chamna siem Lalpa chu;
 Pathien Chapa ngei ahi ie,
 Kalvari thing hansedawla thi kha.

[V2]
 A tho kittai; A tho kit ta ie;
 Chawian un, I Hukdampau a tho tai;
 A melma cheng a nuoisieh zo tai,
 Mi thiengthote tawh kumsawta vaihawm ding.

[V3]
 2. A luong puonnem in a tuom ui,
 Pathien gam kinem ten;
 Huon than awng achun a siel ui,
 Zawhna lopi tawh A hung tho kit tai.

[V4]
 3. Than apatin A tho kit tai,
 Hukdampa Lalpen chu;
 Than thim apatin A hung pawt,
 Khawvel gitloh leh thihna A zo tai.

[V5]
 4. Thihna hatna A nuoisieh tai,
 Galhatpa chawian un;
 Hallellujah ka hukdampa.
 Pakna'n khawvel zailan hung dim kit hen.</lyrics>
<author>Siamliana</author>
<hymn_number>83</hymn_number>
</song>